        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Improving Access to Alternative Pain Management Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows psychological evaluation requirements for Medicare coverage of specified neurostimulation services to be met via telehealth. The bill also expands Medicare coverage to include such telehealth services.</p>]]>
        </text>
